name: 6 Kings - King Amadi
description:
A youth yet wise.
Timid but unafraid.
He has a bloodline that is potent and thick, made from the Fibre of Kings greater than Solomon.
He knew he had a calling to one day fulfill.
His father's had done before and he relished the opportunity to stand for his Tribe. 
He sets forth on his grand mission.
Wisdom, Truth, Protection and Safety are to become his legacy.
